              <tr><td>Images</td><td><code>public/images/</code></td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
          <p><strong>Why This Matters:</strong> Understanding the existing system architecture determines what's possible. Astro + Vercel means simple Git-based updates work perfectly.</p>
        </section>

